articles.title: Fever's Caitlin Clark gets smacked in the eye by Sun rival during playoff game - Fox News
articles.description: Indiana Fever rookie Caitlin Clark was hit in the eye by Connecticut Sun guard DiJonai Carrington during their first-round matchup on Sunday.
articles.content:
Indiana Fever rookie Caitlin Clark was on the receiving end of a hit to the eye from Connecticut Sun guard DiJonai Carrington during their first-round playoff match on Sunday.
